parsed_completion.summary: The content invites employees to a day of winter fun and team building activities at Holmenkollbakken in Oslo on May 30th (Thursday). The day starts with skiing at 10:00 AM, followed by exciting team activities like board games and an 'escape room', and concludes with a delicious dinner and drinks around 11:00 PM. Employees are requested to confirm attendance and inform about any food allergies by May 26th. The CEO is looking forward to creating memories together.

parameters.body: The content invites employees to a day of winter fun and team building activities at Holmenkollbakken in Oslo on May 30th (Thursday). The day starts with skiing at 10:00 AM, followed by exciting team activities like board games and an 'escape room', and concludes with a delicious dinner and drinks around 11:00 PM. Employees are requested to confirm attendance and inform about any food allergies by May 26th. The CEO is looking forward to creating memories together.
parameters.raw_body:
Kjære ansatte,

Vi inviterer deg til en dag med vintermoro og teambygging ved Holmenkollbakken i Oslo. Den 30. mai (torsdag) starter vi dagen med skiglede kl. 10:00. Etterfulgt av en dag med spennende teamaktiviteter som bordspill og 'escape room', avslutter vi arrangementet med en deilig middag og drikke. Arrangementet forventes å vare til rundt kl. 23:00. Vennligst bekreft deltakelse og informer om eventuelle matallergier innen 26. mai.

Ser frem til å skape minner sammen!

Med vennlig hilsen,

Jeff
CEO
